Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:09.15,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Argh... They said it wasn't going to rain today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.24,0:00:13.31,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,"Chain of Robberies Underway"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:32.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:35.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you came out to meet me! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez! It's already past 9 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry... My club ended up staying late...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:44.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.98,0:00:46.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.41,0:01:05.25,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Only the light of deductions can tear apart\Nthe pitch-black shadows and bottomless darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.25,0:01:09.13,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A chain of robberies —\hA coincidental trick has surprising consequences!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:10.67,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:12.71,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.71,0:01:15.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.63,0:02:45.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful though. There's some dangerous guy creeping around here lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.47,0:02:48.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean the hooded robber?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.73,0:02:51.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's known as the hoodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.77,0:02:55.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He attacks women with an extendable baton and steals their bags, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.89,0:03:03.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So far, everyone got off with light injuries, but if he's not caught soon, his crimes might start escalating—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man in a hood went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:19.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.51,0:03:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.63,0:03:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why aren't your clothes wet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.68,0:03:32.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't hurry, he'll get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rain started without warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.09,0:03:38.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your shoes are dirty, and your trousers are wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:43.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it strange that you don't have an umbrella, but your clothes are dry?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, he's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:50.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were wearing something else on top of them, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...a hoodie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.10,0:04:07.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Well, that's the way it goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.15,0:04:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, what about that scream from before?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.94,0:04:18.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you've been a great help, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:42.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't know what to do about the hoodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it was nothing special, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:52.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.79,0:04:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shush, I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, feel free to call if you ever need anything, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.61,0:04:59.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.11,0:05:05.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:07.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.37,0:05:09.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.70,0:05:14.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her CT scan and brainwaves show nothing wrong. The doctor said she could go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.50,0:05:21.55,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mizuki Tachibana (25)\NVictim of the hoodman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.04,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:23.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. I should call my roommate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must be worried about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad you got off with light injuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A small relief hidden in misfortune, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Excuse me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:37.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sato here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.39,0:05:38.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.93,0:05:40.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko—my roommate, she's not answering the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She should've finished work long ago by now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You found a girl's corpse near the crime scene from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:59.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, do you know what Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was wearing a white jacket and a beige skirt...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tachibana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.39,0:06:17.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How could this happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:27.44,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yōko Katsuragi (25)\NMizuki's roommate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.90,0:06:32.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake! That's Yoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was so happy when we said goodbye this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:43.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought that would be the last time I'd see her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.62,0:06:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, you stay with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From looking at her corpse, I'd say she died about one or two hours ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:03.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She worked at a clothing store nearby, and was probably attacked as she was heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was hit on the back of the head with some sort of rod.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The method, area, and time frame all match with the other hoodman victims.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:24.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cash in her purse had been taken too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably intended to just give her light injuries like with the others, but something made him end up killing Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:38.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he attacked Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} without even taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:44.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would have thought two roommates would be attacked one after another?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:48.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that led to us catching the culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe their bond together brought about a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.58,0:08:04.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It smells like coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.88,0:08:08.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn brat, always wandering off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:16.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's everybody going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're taking Tachibana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} back to HQ to hear her story, just to be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should take her statement about the case too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.81,0:08:27.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was thinking I should go with Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wanna come too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:32.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, Uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just to check, that's definitely the man who attacked you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:51.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It was definitely him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.80,0:08:52.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, doesn't he seem angry about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:09:02.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, he confessed that he was\Nbehind the chain of robberies, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.85,0:09:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's completely refusing to admit\Nthat he murdered Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:13.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even when attacking you, Tachibana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, he says that he didn't know what to do because you saw his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but he had no intention of killing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:19.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.79,0:09:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.24,0:09:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're counting on you, Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:26.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, we haven't finished our investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:27.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Detective Takagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've caught the hoodman, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you ladies are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.17,0:09:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Victims of the hoodman!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you'll give us back what he stole, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our purses!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:44.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had my driver's license in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you really been looking for them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:47.89,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We have been looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:47.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.38,0:09:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of you ladies had your purses stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.32,0:09:52.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:54.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:10:01.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The murdered Yoko{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10} only had her money stolen, and her purse was left at the scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'll leave them with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, I'll drive them back safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on, Detective Sato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got a thread on your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:14.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.96,0:10:17.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot to take out the tacking stitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.38,0:10:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tacking stitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Threads called tacking stitches are attached to slits and pleats on new skirts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:32.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To make the fabric keep its shape, the ends are tied together with a knot.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:40.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The skirt I was supposed to wear today broke, so I rushed and bought this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:44.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, Mouri here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:10:59.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.76,0:11:02.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.89,0:11:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blood on the hoodman's extendable baton was found to be Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.06,0:11:12.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.69,0:11:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Now we've even got evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can be sure that Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was killed by the hoodman!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be glad to hear that, Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:27.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It'll make Yoko happy from up in heaven too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.58,0:11:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm stuffed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.57,0:11:37.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, waitress! I'll have another beer and some {\i1}kara'age{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:42.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I just solved a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.63,0:11:45.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you this isn't the proper time and place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} just lost a close friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:50.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not argue, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:12:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko and I used to argue and talk here a lot, so you brought back some memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm glad her killer was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.74,0:12:10.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is all thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's my hand towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:19.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That one's yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.63,0:12:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, I can't believe you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.68,0:12:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. Here, you can have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I'm not using that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it matter? They're all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:38.15,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I see... So that's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've got it, Tachibana{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.28,0:12:47.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, let me. I want to show my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:51.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I wouldn't want it to cause problems for you later, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:54.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so? I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.33,0:12:56.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'll let you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.25,0:12:59.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The total is ¥10,250.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's quite a lot. I-I hope I have enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a real feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.63,0:13:07.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and I know this is a tough time, but don't give up, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:24.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you get lonely, call me anytime...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be right over!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:30.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that, just ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:33.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, I should say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.54,0:13:39.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pain has finally awoken me to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This case is not settled yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not settled, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean that the hoodman wasn't Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:14:01.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? You even said there was evidence earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there's too much that doesn't fit, if he was her murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:07.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't fit?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.90,0:14:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had the cash taken from her purse, and her purse left behind at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.16,0:14:18.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But wasn't he after her money?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:24.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. In the previous three thefts,\Nhe stole the victims' purses too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:26.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why would this time be different?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did think it was odd. But that's hardly enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.85,0:14:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, the wound on the corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was on the left side of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:41.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was attacked from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means the culprit hit Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with the baton in their left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, her killer was left-handed. But the hoodman was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.74,0:14:54.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right-handed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:15:02.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Incidentally, Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, you called her with the phone in your left hand, and used your left hand when you went to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I certainly am left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But so are a lot of other people, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:20.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not finished yet. Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} had a fresh coffee stain on her white inner shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:26.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the stain ended where it met her skirt, and there was no stain on her skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.40,0:15:31.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And her skirt had the tacking stitch attached.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tacking stitch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:41.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tacking stitches are put in new skirts so they keep their shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:46.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had an idea, and decided to check with the manager of the shop Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} worked at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:57.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right when Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was leaving the clothing store for the day, she spilled coffee on her top and skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:03.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because of that, she bought a new jacket and skirt there, and changed into them before leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why the coffee stain on her shirt cuts off, and why her skirt still had the tacking stitch on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.70,0:16:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said this about the dead Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:24.37,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She was so happy when we said goodbye this morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.37,0:16:28.29,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I never thought that would be the last time I'd see her alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.29,0:16:30.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yoko...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.26,0:16:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You hadn't seen Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} since you said goodbye to her this morning, so how did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know about the clothes she wore after work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:42.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-She was probably wearing similar clothes this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.61,0:16:49.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I just mistook them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.68,0:16:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}! Uncle wanted you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.20,0:16:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had her manager send it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a photo of Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} today, before she changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now please tell me, Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.29,0:17:14.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does that look like a white jacket and beige skirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:18.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You did see Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:22.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After she left work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.64,0:17:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, that's not enough to say for sure that Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} murdered Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.97,0:17:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. It is all circumstancial evidence. Nothing decisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.93,0:17:42.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How cruel! You're treating me like a killer just because of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko was a close friend of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.75,0:17:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's right, Dad! If you're going to accuse someone, you should have good evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.88,0:17:52.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good evidence, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, the evidence exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.26,0:17:58.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.26,0:18:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the restaurant, for some reason you put your purse into your pocket, when you had taken it out of your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you put it back into your bag...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.81,0:18:09.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.67,0:18:13.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Afraid of me seeing inside your bag when you put it away...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.98,0:18:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something that you don't want us to see in your bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:25.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right. I thought it was strange when we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.75,0:18:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cold enough tonight that anyone would wear a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your clothes are far too light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.59,0:18:40.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if I assume that you had to take off your coat for some reason, then that would explain your light clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bag probably contains your coat, with Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's not all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hoodman's original extendable baton should be in your bag as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:19:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Then what was the baton the hoodman had?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.52,0:19:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The murder weapon Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} used to kill Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:17.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, to make it look like the work of the hoodman, you researched the extendable baton he always used.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then you bought another baton just like it, and used that extendable baton to kill Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ironically, as you were leaving the scene, you were attacked by the real hoodman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a stroke of bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the chance came to transform that luck from bad to good...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.86,0:19:39.24,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The man in a hood went that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was when you came up with a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The way to use your accident with the hoodman to great advantage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:58.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! So she swapped the hoodman's\Nextendable baton with her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.88,0:20:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why we found Yoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s blood on the hoodman's extendable baton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She even almost deceived me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:12.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the fuss about the hand towels made me realise...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:19.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That perhaps the murder weapon was swapped sometime, just like the hand towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:20.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran hasn't left your side since we rescued you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't had time to dispose of your coat and baton.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:33.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, show us... Show us what's in your bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizuki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.97,0:20:47.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\i1}yōko{\i0} = "child of the sun"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She really was like the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:58.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So bright, so selfish, and everything had to revolve around her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10\i1}mizuki{\i0} = "beautiful moon"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was the sun, and I was just like the powerless moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:08.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that was Yoko's excuse to steal everything from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.78,0:21:15.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She took my clothes, my money, and my boyfriend, all like it was the natural thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:18.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I still held back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I heard her say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.96,0:21:26.63,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, sorry, Mizuki will be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.63,0:21:31.31,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, I wish the hoodman would just do her in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.31,0:21:32.60,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She's such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:40.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I attacked her instead and made it look like it was the hoodman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.24,0:23:10.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You ate my cake as a snack again, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.28,0:23:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It wasn't me! I may have eaten your cakes before, but this time it was really that darn cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.04,0:23:21.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trying to pin the blame on Goro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} again, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You really got away with the perfect crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, you heard that call?{check these lines with DCTP, no CCs}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.09,0:23:41.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The collar's extended, and I can see your bra.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.60,0:23:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is an off-shoulder, and that's the whole point of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.36,0:23:51.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Death by drowning, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.61,0:23:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm taking you into custody for murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:04.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the next Conan: Suspect: Makoto Kyōgoku? (Part I)!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.21,0:24:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Bowling Alley
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:10.80,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,At a bowling alley...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:12.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Karate vs. Jeet Kune Do!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.34,0:24:14.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Why there?!
